description: Feeds is a the ultimate Google Reader client for the Palm WebOS platform. When you read an article on Feeds, Google Reader will be updated. Landscape mode with matching gestures, you can read articles from your Google Reader feed from anywhere. Backup your articles for offline reading and take it on a plane, train, or road trip. With built-in notifications you can be notified when you have unread articles and even have it backup articles while gathering notifications, for automated backups. Email or Message your friends any interesting articles you might find. Feeds even has a light and dark theme!
